<h2 id="message-received">Message Received</h2>

<p>I highly recommend everyone to try to find a willing <a href="#two">(2)</a> in-person mentor who is someone you look up to and hope to achieve something similar one day, and find a way to <a href="https://www.garyvaynerchuk.com/giving-without-expectation/">provide them value</a>.</p>

